{"obs_mrf4mmrw_c8baad9aec93":{"hookType":"subagent_stop","id":"obs_mrf4mmrw_c8baad9aec93","raw":{"agent_id":"a93dc698b2c622186","last_message":"We're setting up the SEONGON LMS project (Laravel API + React SPA + MySQL). The design is approved and I'm ready to write the two spec docs. Next: tell me to write both specs directly, or re-run the parallel agents."},"sessionId":"f6391857-cae2-462f-9b72-4aef8b29d817","timestamp":"2026-07-10T16:04:59.975Z"},"obs_mrf4w24x_06ba0dcb3f58":{"hookType":"post_tool_use","id":"obs_mrf4w24x_06ba0dcb3f58","raw":{"tool_input":{"content":"# SEONGON LMS ‚Äî Backend / System Design Spec\n\n- **Ng√Ýy:** 2026-07-10\n- **Tr·∫°ng th√°i:** Draft (ch·ªù review)\n- **Ph·∫°m vi t√Ýi li·ªáu:** Ki·∫øn tr√∫c h·ªá th·ªëng, data model, **API contract (ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω)**, business rules, payment seam, auth, certificate, v√Ý **to√Ýn b·ªô Docker/Infra**.\n- **Kh√¥ng thu·ªôc t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy:** Chi ti·∫øt frontend React (n·∫±m ·ªü `2026-07-10-seongon-lms-frontend-design.md`). ·ªû ƒë√¢y frontend ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi chung l√Ý \"SPA client\".\n- **ƒê·∫∑c t·∫£ g·ªëc:** [`SPEC/Draft.md`](../../../SPEC/Draft.md) (User Story, actors, s∆° ƒë·ªì Use Case H√¨nh 3.4, Activity H√¨nh 3.1 & 3.2).\n\n---\n\n## 1. T·ªïng quan & m·ª•c ti√™u\n\nSEONGON LMS l√Ý n·ªÅn t·∫£ng **b√°n v√Ý h·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc tr·ª±c tuy·∫øn** cho c√¥ng ty SEONGON. Backend l√Ý m·ªôt **REST API** (Laravel 12) ph·ª•c v·ª• m·ªôt SPA client t√°ch r·ªùi, d·ªØ li·ªáu l∆∞u trong **MySQL 8**.\n\n**3 t√°c nh√¢n (actors):**\n\n| Actor | M√¥ t·∫£ | Tr·∫°ng th√°i auth |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Guest (Kh√°ch)** | Xem/t√¨m kh√≥a h·ªçc, xem chi ti·∫øt, ƒëƒÉng k√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | Ch∆∞a ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p (kh√¥ng token) |\n| **Student (H·ªçc vi√™n)** | Mua kh√≥a (thanh to√°n mock), h·ªçc video, theo d√µi ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (ƒë·∫°t ‚â• 75%), nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ, ƒë√°nh gi√° | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=student` |\n| **Admin (Qu·∫£n tr·ªã vi√™n)** | Qu·∫£n l√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, danh m·ª•c, kh√≥a h·ªçc, b√Ýi h·ªçc, b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra/ng√¢n h√Ýng c√¢u h·ªèi, ƒë√°nh gi√°, dashboard th·ªëng k√™ | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=admin` |\n\n**M·ª•c ti√™u backend:** cung c·∫•p API ƒë·∫ßy ƒë·ªß cho to√Ýn b·ªô User Story trong SPEC, th·ª±c thi ƒë√∫ng c√°c business rule (enrollment 1 nƒÉm, ch·∫∑n thi khi ch∆∞a 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, ng∆∞·ª°ng ƒë·∫°t 75%, c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ), v√Ý c√≥ th·ªÉ test t·ª± ƒë·ªông ƒë∆∞·ª£c.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Tech stack (Backend)\n\n| Th√Ýnh ph·∫ßn | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\n|---|---|\n| Ng√¥n ng·ªØ / Framework | PHP 8.3 ¬∑ **Laravel 12** |\n| Auth | **Laravel Sanctum** (Bearer token cho SPA t√°ch origin) |\n| Database | **MySQL 8** |\n| PDF ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` |\n| Test | **Pest** (tr√™n PHPUnit) + factories + seeders |\n| Ch·∫°y local | Docker Compose (mysql) + `php artisan serve`, ho·∫∑c full-docker |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Ki·∫øn tr√∫c & t·ªï ch·ª©c code\n\n**Ki·ªÉu ki·∫øn tr√∫c: layered chu·∫©n Laravel.** Lu·ªìng m·ªôt request:\n\n```\nRoute (/api/v1/...) ‚Üí Controller (m·ªèng) ‚Üí FormRequest (validate)\n      ‚Üí Service (business logic) ‚Üí Eloquent Model ‚Üí DB\n      ‚Üí API Resource (ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng JSON response)\nAuthorization: middleware (auth:sanctum, role:admin) + Policy\n```\n\nController ch·ªâ ƒëi·ªÅu ph·ªëi; **to√Ýn b·ªô nghi·ªáp v·ª• n·∫±m trong Service** ƒë·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng v√Ý test ƒë·ªôc l·∫≠p.\n\n**B·ªë c·ª•c th∆∞ m·ª•c `BE/app/`:**\n\n```\napp/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Http/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Controllers/Api/\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Public/      # Auth (register/login), Course, Category c√¥ng khai\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Student/     # Order, Enrollment, Lesson, Quiz, Review, Certificate\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Admin/       # User, Category, Course, Lesson, Quiz, Question, Review, Dashboard\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Requests/        # FormRequest cho t·ª´ng action (validate)\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Resources/       # API Resource (CourseResource, LessonResource, ...)\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Middleware/       # EnsureRole (role:admin)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Models/              # Eloquent models + quan h·ªá\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Services/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ EnrollmentService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ProgressService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ QuizGradingService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CertificateService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Payment/\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentGateway.php      # interface\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ MockGateway.php         # implementation hi·ªán t·∫°i\n‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentResult.php       # DTO k·∫øt qu·∫£\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Policies/            # EnrollmentPolicy, ReviewPolicy, ...\n```\n\n**C√°c Service v√Ý tr√°ch nhi·ªám:**\n\n| Service | Tr√°ch nhi·ªám |\n|---|---|\n| `EnrollmentService` | Sau khi order `paid`: t·∫°o `enrollment` v·ªõi `enrolled_at = now`, `expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `status = active`. Ki·ªÉm tra h·∫øt h·∫°n. |\n| `Payment\\PaymentGateway` (interface) + `MockGateway` | X·ª≠ l√Ω thanh to√°n gi·∫£ l·∫≠p, tr·∫£ `PaymentResult` (success/failure). Seam ƒë·ªÉ thay driver th·∫≠t sau. |\n| `ProgressService` | Ghi nh·∫≠n ho√Ýn th√Ýnh lesson, t√≠nh `progress% = completed / total`, ki·ªÉm tra ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán ƒë·ªß 100% ƒë·ªÉ m·ªü b√Ýi thi. |\n| `QuizGradingService` | Ch·∫•m b√Ýi, t√≠nh ƒëi·ªÉm, so `pass_score`, qu·∫£n l√Ω `attempt_no` vs `max_attempts`. |\n| `CertificateService` | Khi ƒë·∫°t: sinh `certificate_code` (unique), render PDF (dompdf), l∆∞u `pdf_path`. |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Data model (MySQL)\n\n14 b·∫£ng nghi·ªáp v·ª•. Ngo√Ýi ra Laravel/Sanctum t·ª± t·∫°o: `personal_access_tokens` (Sanctum), `password_reset_tokens`, `sessions`, `cache`, `jobs`, `failed_jobs`.\n\nK√Ω hi·ªáu: **PK** = kh√≥a ch√≠nh (id, bigint auto-increment), **FK** = kh√≥a ngo·∫°i, *ts* = `created_at`/`updated_at`.\n\n### 4.1. `users`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| name | varchar | not null |\n| email | varchar | **unique**, not null |\n| email_verified_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| password | varchar | not null (hashed) |\n| role | enum('student','admin') | default 'student' |\n| phone | varchar | nullable |\n| avatar | varchar | nullable (URL) |\n| status | enum('active','locked') | default 'active' |\n| remember_token | varchar | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.2. `categories`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| name | varchar | not null |\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\n| description | text | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.3. `courses`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| category_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí categories, index |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\n| description | longtext | nullable |\n| thumbnail | varchar | nullable |\n| price | decimal(10,2) | default 0 |\n| instructor_name | varchar | nullable |\n| instructor_bio | text | nullable |\n| level | enum('beginner','intermediate','advanced') | nullable |\n| status | enum('draft','published') | default 'draft', index |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.4. `lessons`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| video_url | varchar | not null (embed YouTube/Vimeo) |\n| description | text | nullable |\n| duration | int | nullable (gi√¢y) |\n| position | int | not null (th·ª© t·ª± trong kh√≥a) |\n| *ts* | | index `(course_id, position)` |\n\n### 4.5. `orders`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| amount | decimal(10,2) | not null (snapshot gi√° l√∫c mua) |\n| status | enum('pending','paid','failed') | default 'pending', index |\n| payment_method | enum('card','qr') | nullable |\n| transaction_ref | varchar | nullable |\n| paid_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| *ts* | | index `(user_id, status)` |\n\n### 4.6. `enrollments`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| order_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí orders, nullable |\n| enrolled_at | timestamp | not null |\n| expires_at | timestamp | not null (= enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm) |\n| status | enum('active','expired') | default 'active' |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`**, index `expires_at` |\n\n### 4.7. `lesson_progress`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\n| lesson_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí lessons |\n| is_completed | boolean | default false |\n| completed_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(enrollment_id, lesson_id)`** |\n\n### 4.8. `quizzes`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, **unique** (1 b√Ýi thi cu·ªëi/kh√≥a) |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| pass_score | int | default 75 (%) |\n| max_attempts | int | default 3 |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.9. `questions`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes, index |\n| content | text | not null |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.10. `question_options`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| question_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí questions, index |\n| content | varchar | not null |\n| is_correct | boolean | default false |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.11. `quiz_attempts`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes |\n| score | int | not null (0‚Äì100) |\n| passed | boolean | not null |\n| attempt_no | int | not null (l·∫ßn thi th·ª© m·∫•y) |\n| submitted_at | timestamp | not null |\n| *ts* | | index `(enrollment_id, quiz_id)` |\n\n### 4.12. `quiz_attempt_answers`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| quiz_attempt_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quiz_attempts |\n| question_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí questions |\n| selected_option_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí question_options, nullable |\n| is_correct | boolean | not null |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.13. `reviews`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, index |\n| rating | tinyint | 1‚Äì5, not null |\n| comment | text | nullable |\n| status | enum('visible','hidden') | default 'visible' |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`** |\n\n### 4.14. `certificates`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments, **unique** |\n| certificate_code | varchar | **unique** (vd `SEONGON-2026-000123`) |\n| issued_at | timestamp | not null |\n| pdf_path | varchar | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.15. Quan h·ªá (relationships)\n\n- **User** hasMany `orders`, `enrollments`, `reviews`.\n- **Category** hasMany `courses`.\n- **Course** belongsTo `category`; hasMany `lessons`, `orders`, `enrollments`, `reviews`; hasOne `quiz`.\n- **Lesson** belongsTo `course`; hasMany `lesson_progress`.\n- **Order** belongsTo `user`, `course`; hasOne `enrollment`.\n- **Enrollment** belongsTo `user`, `course`, `order`; hasMany `lesson_progress`, `quiz_attempts`; hasOne `certificate`.\n- **Quiz** belongsTo `course`; hasMany `questions`, `quiz_attempts`.\n- **Question** belongsTo `quiz`; hasMany `question_options`.\n- **QuizAttempt** belongsTo `enrollment`, `quiz`; hasMany `quiz_attempt_answers`.\n- **Review** belongsTo `user`, `course`.\n- **Certificate** belongsTo `enrollment`.\n\n---\n\n## 5. API contract (`/api/v1`) ‚Äî AUTHORITATIVE\n\nƒê√¢y l√Ý ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω cho to√Ýn b·ªô endpoint. Frontend spec ch·ªâ tham chi·∫øu, kh√¥ng ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l·∫°i.\n\n**Quy ∆∞·ªõc chung:**\n- Base URL: `/api/v1`. Response JSON.\n- Auth: header `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.\n- Danh s√°ch c√≥ ph√¢n trang: `{ data: [...], meta: { current_page, last_page, per_page, total } }`.\n- L·ªói: `422` (validation, k√®m `errors`), `401` (ch∆∞a auth), `403` (kh√¥ng ƒë·ªß quy·ªÅn / kh√≥a h·∫øt h·∫°n), `404` (kh√¥ng t·ªìn t·∫°i). Envelope l·ªói: `{ message, errors? }`.\n\n### 5.1. Public (kh√¥ng c·∫ßn auth)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/auth/register` | ƒêƒÉng k√Ω h·ªçc vi√™n | `{name,email,password,password_confirmation}` | `{user, token}` |\n| POST | `/auth/login` | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p | `{email,password}` | `{user, token}` |\n| GET | `/categories` | Danh s√°ch danh m·ª•c | ‚Äî | `[category]` |\n| GET | `/courses` | Danh s√°ch + t√¨m ki·∫øm/l·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc `published` | query: `q, category, min_price, max_price, sort, page` | paginated `[course]` |\n| GET | `/courses/{slug}` | Chi ti·∫øt kh√≥a (k√®m lessons preview, quiz info, rating t·ªïng) | ‚Äî | `course` |\n| GET | `/courses/{slug}/reviews` | ƒê√°nh gi√° c·ªßa kh√≥a (ch·ªâ `visible`) | query: `page` | paginated `[review]` |\n\n### 5.2. Authenticated (student | admin)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/auth/logout` | Thu h·ªìi token hi·ªán t·∫°i | ‚Äî | `204` |\n| GET | `/auth/me` | Th√¥ng tin user ƒëang ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | ‚Äî | `user` |\n| PUT | `/auth/profile` | C·∫≠p nh·∫≠t h·ªì s∆° | `{name,phone,avatar?}` | `user` |\n| PUT | `/auth/password` | ƒê·ªïi m·∫≠t kh·∫©u | `{current_password,password,password_confirmation}` | `204` |\n\n### 5.3. Student\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/orders` | T·∫°o ƒë∆°n mua kh√≥a (status `pending`) | `{course_id}` | `order` |\n| POST | `/orders/{id}/pay` | Thanh to√°n (mock) | `{payment_method:'card'|'qr', outcome?:'success'|'failure'}` | `{order, enrollment?}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses` | Kh√≥a ƒë√£ ƒëƒÉng k√Ω (k√®m progress, tr·∫°ng th√°i h·∫øt h·∫°n) | query: `page` | paginated `[enrollment+course]` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/lessons` | B√Ýi h·ªçc c·ªßa kh√≥a + tr·∫°ng th√°i ho√Ýn th√Ýnh | ‚Äî | `[lesson+is_completed]` |\n| POST | `/my/lessons/{lesson}/complete` | ƒê√°nh d·∫•u ho√Ýn th√Ýnh 1 lesson | ‚Äî | `{progress}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/progress` | Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô (%), ƒë·ªß ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán thi ch∆∞a | ‚Äî | `{completed,total,percent,can_take_exam}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/quiz` | ƒê·ªÅ thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (c√¢u h·ªèi + options, **·∫©n** `is_correct`) | ‚Äî | `quiz+questions` |\n| POST | `/my/courses/{course}/quiz/attempts` | N·ªôp b√Ýi thi, ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm | `{answers:[{question_id,option_id}]}` | `{attempt, passed, score, certificate?}` |\n| GET | `/my/quiz-attempts/{attempt}` | Xem k·∫øt qu·∫£ chi ti·∫øt (ƒë√∫ng/sai t·ª´ng c√¢u) | ‚Äî | `attempt+answers` |\n| POST | `/my/courses/{course}/reviews` | ƒê√°nh gi√° kh√≥a (sau khi c√≥ enrollment) | `{rating,comment?}` | `review` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/certificate` | T·∫£i ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ PDF | ‚Äî | `application/pdf` |\n\n### 5.4. Admin (`/admin`, middleware `role:admin`)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/admin/users` | Danh s√°ch h·ªçc vi√™n (filter/search) |\n| PATCH | `/admin/users/{id}/status` | K√≠ch ho·∫°t / kh√≥a t√Ýi kho·∫£n (`{status}`) |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/categories` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/categories/{id}` | CRUD danh m·ª•c |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/courses` ¬∑ GET/PUT/DELETE `/admin/courses/{id}` | CRUD kh√≥a h·ªçc |\n| PATCH | `/admin/courses/{id}/publish` | Xu·∫•t b·∫£n / ·∫©n kh√≥a (`{status}`) |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/courses/{course}/lessons` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/lessons/{id}` | CRUD b√Ýi h·ªçc |\n| PATCH | `/admin/courses/{course}/lessons/reorder` | S·∫Øp x·∫øp l·∫°i th·ª© t·ª± (`{order:[lesson_id...]}`) |\n| POST/PUT | `/admin/courses/{course}/quiz` | T·∫°o/s·ª≠a b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra (title, pass_score, max_attempts) |\n| POST | `/admin/quizzes/{quiz}/questions` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/questions/{id}` | CRUD c√¢u h·ªèi + ƒë√°p √°n (options l·ªìng trong payload) |\n| GET | `/admin/reviews` ¬∑ PATCH `/admin/reviews/{id}/status` ¬∑ DELETE `/admin/reviews/{id}` | Duy·ªát/·∫©n/x√≥a ƒë√°nh gi√° |\n| GET | `/admin/dashboard/stats` | Th·ªëng k√™: s·ªë h·ªçc vi√™n, s·ªë kh√≥a, t·ª∑ l·ªá ho√Ýn th√Ýnh, doanh thu (t·ªïng `orders.amount` v·ªõi `status=paid`) |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Business rules\n\n√Ånh x·∫° tr·ª±c ti·∫øp c√°c s∆° ƒë·ªì Activity trong SPEC (H√¨nh 3.1 ‚Äì thanh to√°n, H√¨nh 3.2 ‚Äì h·ªçc).\n\n**BR-1 ‚Äî Mua kh√≥a & thanh to√°n (H√¨nh 3.1):**\n1. `POST /orders` t·∫°o order `pending` (amount = gi√° kh√≥a hi·ªán t·∫°i).\n2. `POST /orders/{id}/pay` g·ªçi `MockGateway`.\n   - **Success:** order ‚Üí `paid` + `paid_at`; `EnrollmentService` t·∫°o `enrollment` (`expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `active`); (song song, theo s∆° ƒë·ªì fork/join) ghi nh·∫≠n v√Ý g·ª≠i th√¥ng b√°o + h√≥a ƒë∆°n (mock/log/notification). Tr·∫£ v·ªÅ `{order, enrollment}`.\n   - **Failure:** order ‚Üí `failed`; h·ªçc vi√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ **th·ª≠ l·∫°i** (`pay` l·∫ßn n·ªØa) ho·∫∑c **h·ªßy** (d·ª´ng lu·ªìng). Tr·∫£ `422/200` k√®m th√¥ng b√°o l·ªói.\n3. Kh√¥ng cho mua n·∫øu ƒë√£ c√≥ enrollment `active` cho kh√≥a ƒë√≥ (unique `(user_id,course_id)`).\n\n**BR-2 ‚Äî Gating truy c·∫≠p h·ªçc:** m·ªçi endpoint `/my/courses/{course}/*` y√™u c·∫ßu enrollment `active` **v√Ý** `expires_at >= now`. N·∫øu `expires_at < now` ‚Üí ƒë√°nh d·∫•u `expired` ‚Üí tr·∫£ `403` (\"kh√≥a ƒë√£ h·∫øt h·∫°n\"). (H√¨nh 3.2, nh√°nh \"Kh√≥a h·ªçc c√≤n h·∫°n?\").\n\n**BR-3 ‚Äî Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô:** `POST /my/lessons/{lesson}/complete` upsert `lesson_progress.is_completed = true`. `progress% = s·ªë lesson completed / t·ªïng lesson c·ªßa kh√≥a`.\n\n**BR-4 ‚Äî Gating thi:** ch·ªâ cho ph√©p `POST .../quiz/attempts` khi `progress = 100%` (`can_take_exam = true`). Ch∆∞a ƒë·ªß ‚Üí `403`. (H√¨nh 3.2, nh√°nh \"ƒê·∫°t 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô?\").\n\n**BR-5 ‚Äî Ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm:** `score = (s·ªë c√¢u ƒë√∫ng / t·ªïng c√¢u) * 100`. `passed = score >= quiz.pass_score` (m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh **75**). `attempt_no` tƒÉng d·∫ßn; n·∫øu `attempt_no > max_attempts` ‚Üí ch·∫∑n n·ªôp th√™m (`422`). Ch∆∞a ƒë·∫°t ‚Üí th√¥ng b√°o cho thi l·∫°i (trong gi·ªõi h·∫°n `max_attempts`). (H√¨nh 3.2, \"ƒêi·ªÉm thi ‚â• 75%?\").\n\n**BR-6 ‚Äî C·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ:** l·∫ßn **ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n** `passed = true`, `CertificateService` t·∫°o `certificate` (`certificate_code` unique) + render PDF. Idempotent: ƒë√£ c√≥ ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ th√¨ kh√¥ng t·∫°o l·∫°i.\n\n**BR-7 ‚Äî ƒê√°nh gi√°:** `POST .../reviews` l√Ý **t√πy ch·ªçn**, cho h·ªçc vi√™n ƒë√£ c√≥ enrollment; unique `(user_id, course_id)` (m·ªói kh√≥a ƒë√°nh gi√° 1 l·∫ßn, c√≥ th·ªÉ c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t).\n\n> **‚öÝÔ∏è M√¢u thu·∫´n trong SPEC (gi·ªØ l·∫°i ƒë·ªÉ ƒë·ªëi chi·∫øu):** ph·∫ßn vƒÉn b·∫£n ¬ß3.2.2.2 n√≥i h·ªçc vi√™n \"*ph·∫£i ƒë√°nh gi√° kh√≥a h·ªçc ƒë·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ*\", nh∆∞ng **s∆° ƒë·ªì H√¨nh 3.2 v·∫Ω ng∆∞·ª£c l·∫°i**: c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ **tr∆∞·ªõc**, r·ªìi ƒë√°nh gi√° l√Ý b∆∞·ªõc **t√πy ch·ªçn cu·ªëi**. ‚Üí Tri·ªÉn khai **theo s∆° ƒë·ªì** (cert tr∆∞·ªõc, rating optional). N·∫øu c√¥ng ty mu·ªën theo vƒÉn b·∫£n, ch·ªâ c·∫ßn ƒë·∫£o th·ª© t·ª± ·ªü BR-6/BR-7 ‚Äî ghi nh·∫≠n l√Ý ƒëi·ªÉm c·∫ßn ch·ªët v·ªõi PM.\n\n---\n\n## 7. Payment seam (mock, c√≥ th·ªÉ thay)\n\nThanh to√°n ƒë∆∞·ª£c tr·ª´u t∆∞·ª£ng h√≥a ƒë·ªÉ **kh√¥ng kh√≥a c·ª©ng** v√Ýo m·ªôt c·ªïng c·ª• th·ªÉ:\n\n```php\ninterface PaymentGateway {\n    public function charge(Order $order, array $data): PaymentResult;\n}\n\nfinal class PaymentResult {\n    public bool $success;\n    public ?string $transactionRef;\n    public ?string $message;\n}\n```\n\n- **`MockGateway`** (driver hi·ªán t·∫°i): quy·∫øt ƒë·ªãnh success/failure theo input `outcome` (m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng dev/demo); sinh `transaction_ref` gi·∫£. Kh√¥ng g·ªçi m·∫°ng.\n- ƒêƒÉng k√Ω qua container: `PaymentGateway::class ‚Üí MockGateway::class` trong `AppServiceProvider`.\n- **VNPay l√Ý driver t∆∞∆°ng lai** (`VnpayGateway implements PaymentGateway`): ch·ªâ c·∫ßn th√™m class + ƒë·ªïi binding, **kh√¥ng s·ª≠a** `EnrollmentService`/controller. **Kh√¥ng thi·∫øt k·∫ø chi ti·∫øt VNPay ·ªü giai ƒëo·∫°n n√Ýy (YAGNI).**\n\n---\n\n## 8. Auth & ph√¢n quy·ªÅn\n\n- **Sanctum token:** `register`/`login` tr·∫£ `{user, token}` (`personal_access_tokens`). Client g·ª≠i `Authorization: Bearer <token>`. `logout` thu h·ªìi token hi·ªán t·∫°i.\n- **Roles:** `student` (m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh khi ƒëƒÉng k√Ω) v√Ý `admin` (t·∫°o qua seeder, kh√¥ng ƒëƒÉng k√Ω c√¥ng khai). Guest = request kh√¥ng c√≥ token.\n- **Middleware `role:admin`** (`EnsureRole`) b·∫£o v·ªá nh√≥m `/admin/*`.\n- **Policies:** `EnrollmentPolicy` (h·ªçc vi√™n ch·ªâ truy c·∫≠p enrollment/kh√≥a c·ªßa ch√≠nh m√¨nh), `ReviewPolicy`. Ki·ªÉm tra tr·∫°ng th√°i t√Ýi kho·∫£n: `status=locked` ‚Üí ch·∫∑n ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p/t·ª´ ch·ªëi request (`403`).\n\n---\n\n## 9. Certificate (ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ)\n\n- K√≠ch ho·∫°t t·∫°i BR-6. `certificate_code` ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng `SEONGON-{year}-{seq}` (unique).\n- Render PDF b·∫±ng `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` t·ª´ Blade template (t√™n h·ªçc vi√™n, t√™n kh√≥a, ng√Ýy c·∫•p, m√£ ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ). L∆∞u `pdf_path` (storage) ho·∫∑c render on-the-fly.\n- `GET /my/courses/{course}/certificate` tr·∫£ file PDF (ch·ªâ ch·ªß s·ªü h·ªØu enrollment).\n\n---\n\n## 10. Infra / Docker\n\n`Infra/docker-compose.yml` (t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy s·ªü h·ªØu to√Ýn b·ªô ph·∫ßn Docker):\n\n| Service | Image / Build | Vai tr√≤ | Port |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `mysql` | `mysql:8.0` | Database. Env: `MYSQL_DATABASE=seongon_lms`, `MYSQL_USER`, `MYSQL_PASSWORD`, `MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD`. Volume `mysql_data`. | 3306 |\n| `backend` | build `Infra/backend.Dockerfile` (PHP 8.3-fpm + composer, nginx) ‚Äî ho·∫∑c dev: `php artisan serve`. Mount `../BE`. | Laravel API | 8000 |\n| `frontend` | `node:22` (Vite dev) ho·∫∑c build ‚Üí nginx serve. Mount `../FE`. | SPA client | 5173 (dev) / 80 (prod) |\n| `phpmyadmin` *(t√πy ch·ªçn)* | `phpmyadmin` | Qu·∫£n tr·ªã DB qua web | 8080 |\n\n**Bi·∫øn m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng ch√≠nh (`BE/.env`):** `APP_URL=http://localhost:8000`, `DB_CONNECTION=mysql`, `DB_HOST=mysql` (trong docker) / `127.0.0.1` (local), `DB_DATABASE=seongon_lms`, `DB_USERNAME`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `SANCTUM_STATEFUL_DOMAINS`, `FRONTEND_URL`.\n\n**Hai c√°ch ch·∫°y dev:**\n1. **Full-docker:** `docker compose up` ‚Äî c·∫£ mysql + backend + frontend.\n2. **Nh·∫π:** ch·ªâ ch·∫°y `mysql` b·∫±ng Docker, c√≤n `php artisan serve` (BE) v√Ý `npm run dev` (FE) ch·∫°y tr·ª±c ti·∫øp tr√™n m√°y.\n\nCORS c·∫•u h√¨nh cho ph√©p origin c·ªßa FE (`http://localhost:5173`).\n\n---\n\n## 11. Testing (Backend)\n\n**Pest feature tests** (ch·∫°y tr√™n DB test, m·ªói test refresh). Danh s√°ch t·ªëi thi·ªÉu:\n\n| Nh√≥m | Test |\n|---|---|\n| Auth | register t·∫°o user+token; login ƒë√∫ng/sai; login khi `locked` b·ªã ch·∫∑n; ƒë·ªïi m·∫≠t kh·∫©u; logout thu h·ªìi token |\n| Catalog | list courses ch·ªâ `published`; filter theo `q`/`category`/kho·∫£ng gi√°; chi ti·∫øt theo slug |\n| Mua kh√≥a | t·∫°o order pending; pay **success** ‚Üí order paid + t·∫°o enrollment 1 nƒÉm; pay **failure** ‚Üí order failed, cho retry; kh√¥ng cho mua tr√πng khi ƒë√£ enroll |\n| Enrollment | `expires_at = enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm`; d√πng `travel()` gi·∫£ l·∫≠p qu√° 1 nƒÉm ‚Üí truy c·∫≠p h·ªçc tr·∫£ `403` |\n| Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô | complete lesson c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t progress%; unique kh√¥ng nh√¢n ƒë√¥i |\n| Thi | ch·∫∑n thi khi progress < 100%; ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm ƒë√∫ng; `passed` khi ‚â•75%; `attempt_no` tƒÉng; ch·∫∑n khi v∆∞·ª£t `max_attempts` |\n| Ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | ƒë·∫°t l·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ‚Üí t·∫°o certificate + code unique; ƒë√£ c√≥ th√¨ kh√¥ng t·∫°o l·∫°i; ch·ªâ ch·ªß s·ªü h·ªØu t·∫£i ƒë∆∞·ª£c |\n| Review | t·∫°o review unique theo (user,course) |\n| Admin & ph√¢n quy·ªÅn | CRUD category/course/lesson/quiz/question; `role:admin` ch·∫∑n student; dashboard stats tr·∫£ ƒë√∫ng s·ªë li·ªáu |\n\n**Fixtures:** Factories cho m·ªçi model; **Seeder** t·∫°o s·∫µn 1 admin, v√Ýi category, v√Ýi course + lessons + 1 quiz + questions/options ƒë·ªÉ dev/demo.\n\n---\n\n## 12. Non-goals / h∆∞·ªõng m·ªü r·ªông\n\n- T√≠ch h·ª£p c·ªïng thanh to√°n th·∫≠t (VNPay/MoMo) ‚Äî ch·ªâ ch·ª´a seam.\n- Upload/stream video (S3/MinIO) ‚Äî hi·ªán d√πng embed URL.\n- ƒêa ng√¥n ng·ªØ (i18n), th√¥ng b√°o real-time, email th·∫≠t (hi·ªán log/notification mock).\n- H·ªçc vi√™n nhi·ªÅu vai tr√≤ / ph√¢n quy·ªÅn chi ti·∫øt (RBAC n√¢ng cao) ‚Äî hi·ªán 2 role ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n.\n\n---\n\n## Ph·ª• l·ª•c ‚Äî quy·∫øt ƒë·ªãnh ƒë√£ ch·ªët\n\n| H·∫°ng m·ª•c | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\n|---|---|\n| Backend | Laravel 12, PHP 8.3, Sanctum token |\n| Database | MySQL 8 |\n| Payment | Mock (seam `PaymentGateway`, VNPay ƒë·ªÉ sau) |\n| Video | Embed URL (YouTube/Vimeo) |\n| Ki·∫øn tr√∫c code | Layered: Controller ‚Üí FormRequest ‚Üí Service ‚Üí Model ‚Üí Resource |\n| Frontend | (t√Ýi li·ªáu ri√™ng) React 19 + Vite + TS + Tailwind |\n","file_path":"D:\\CODE\\seongon-lms\\docs\\superpowers\\specs\\2026-07-10-seongon-lms-backend-design.md"},"tool_name":"Write","tool_output":"{\"type\":\"create\",\"filePath\":\"D:/CODE/seongon-lms/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-10-seongon-lms-backend-design.md\",\"content\":\"# SEONGON LMS ‚Äî Backend / System Design Spec\\n\\n- **Ng√Ýy:** 2026-07-10\\n- **Tr·∫°ng th√°i:** Draft (ch·ªù review)\\n- **Ph·∫°m vi t√Ýi li·ªáu:** Ki·∫øn tr√∫c h·ªá th·ªëng, data model, **API contract (ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω)**, business rules, payment seam, auth, certificate, v√Ý **to√Ýn b·ªô Docker/Infra**.\\n- **Kh√¥ng thu·ªôc t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy:** Chi ti·∫øt frontend React (n·∫±m ·ªü `2026-07-10-seongon-lms-frontend-design.md`). ·ªû ƒë√¢y frontend ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi chung l√Ý \\\"SPA client\\\".\\n- **ƒê·∫∑c t·∫£ g·ªëc:** [`SPEC/Draft.md`](../../../SPEC/Draft.md) (User Story, actors, s∆° ƒë·ªì Use Case H√¨nh 3.4, Activity H√¨nh 3.1 & 3.2).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. T·ªïng quan & m·ª•c ti√™u\\n\\nSEONGON LMS l√Ý n·ªÅn t·∫£ng **b√°n v√Ý h·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc tr·ª±c tuy·∫øn** cho c√¥ng ty SEONGON. Backend l√Ý m·ªôt **REST API** (Laravel 12) ph·ª•c v·ª• m·ªôt SPA client t√°ch r·ªùi, d·ªØ li·ªáu l∆∞u trong **MySQL 8**.\\n\\n**3 t√°c nh√¢n (actors):**\\n\\n| Actor | M√¥ t·∫£ | Tr·∫°ng th√°i auth |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| **Guest (Kh√°ch)** | Xem/t√¨m kh√≥a h·ªçc, xem chi ti·∫øt, ƒëƒÉng k√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | Ch∆∞a ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p (kh√¥ng token) |\\n| **Student (H·ªçc vi√™n)** | Mua kh√≥a (thanh to√°n mock), h·ªçc video, theo d√µi ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (ƒë·∫°t ‚â• 75%), nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ, ƒë√°nh gi√° | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=student` |\\n| **Admin (Qu·∫£n tr·ªã vi√™n)** | Qu·∫£n l√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, danh m·ª•c, kh√≥a h·ªçc, b√Ýi h·ªçc, b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra/ng√¢n h√Ýng c√¢u h·ªèi, ƒë√°nh gi√°, dashboard th·ªëng k√™ | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=admin` |\\n\\n**M·ª•c ti√™u backend:** cung c·∫•p API ƒë·∫ßy ƒë·ªß cho to√Ýn b·ªô User Story trong SPEC, th·ª±c thi ƒë√∫ng c√°c business rule (enrollment 1 nƒÉm, ch·∫∑n thi khi ch∆∞a 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, ng∆∞·ª°ng ƒë·∫°t 75%, c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ), v√Ý c√≥ th·ªÉ test t·ª± ƒë·ªông ƒë∆∞·ª£c.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Tech stack (Backend)\\n\\n| Th√Ýnh ph·∫ßn | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\\n|---|---|\\n| Ng√¥n ng·ªØ / Framework | PHP 8.3 ¬∑ **Laravel 12** |\\n| Auth | **Laravel Sanctum** (Bearer token cho SPA t√°ch origin) |\\n| Database | **MySQL 8** |\\n| PDF ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` |\\n| Test | **Pest** (tr√™n PHPUnit) + factories + seeders |\\n| Ch·∫°y local | Docker Compose (mysql) + `php artisan serve`, ho·∫∑c full-docker |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Ki·∫øn tr√∫c & t·ªï ch·ª©c code\\n\\n**Ki·ªÉu ki·∫øn tr√∫c: layered chu·∫©n Laravel.** Lu·ªìng m·ªôt request:\\n\\n```\\nRoute (/api/v1/...) ‚Üí Controller (m·ªèng) ‚Üí FormRequest (validate)\\n      ‚Üí Service (business logic) ‚Üí Eloquent Model ‚Üí DB\\n      ‚Üí API Resource (ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng JSON response)\\nAuthorization: middleware (auth:sanctum, role:admin) + Policy\\n```\\n\\nController ch·ªâ ƒëi·ªÅu ph·ªëi; **to√Ýn b·ªô nghi·ªáp v·ª• n·∫±m trong Service** ƒë·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng v√Ý test ƒë·ªôc l·∫≠p.\\n\\n**B·ªë c·ª•c th∆∞ m·ª•c `BE/app/`:**\\n\\n```\\napp/\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Http/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Controllers/Api/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Public/      # Auth (register/login), Course, Category c√¥ng khai\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Student/     # Order, Enrollment, Lesson, Quiz, Review, Certificate\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Admin/       # User, Category, Course, Lesson, Quiz, Question, Review, Dashboard\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Requests/        # FormRequest cho t·ª´ng action (validate)\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Resources/       # API Resource (CourseResource, LessonResource, ...)\\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Middleware/       # EnsureRole (role:admin)\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Models/              # Eloquent models + quan h·ªá\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Services/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ EnrollmentService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ProgressService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ QuizGradingService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CertificateService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Payment/\\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentGateway.php      # interface\\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ MockGateway.php         # implementation hi·ªán t·∫°i\\n‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentResult.php       # DTO k·∫øt qu·∫£\\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Policies/            # EnrollmentPolicy, ReviewPolicy, ...\\n```\\n\\n**C√°c Service v√Ý tr√°ch nhi·ªám:**\\n\\n| Service | Tr√°ch nhi·ªám |\\n|---|---|\\n| `EnrollmentService` | Sau khi order `paid`: t·∫°o `enrollment` v·ªõi `enrolled_at = now`, `expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `status = active`. Ki·ªÉm tra h·∫øt h·∫°n. |\\n| `Payment\\\\PaymentGateway` (interface) + `MockGateway` | X·ª≠ l√Ω thanh to√°n gi·∫£ l·∫≠p, tr·∫£ `PaymentResult` (success/failure). Seam ƒë·ªÉ thay driver th·∫≠t sau. |\\n| `ProgressService` | Ghi nh·∫≠n ho√Ýn th√Ýnh lesson, t√≠nh `progress% = completed / total`, ki·ªÉm tra ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán ƒë·ªß 100% ƒë·ªÉ m·ªü b√Ýi thi. |\\n| `QuizGradingService` | Ch·∫•m b√Ýi, t√≠nh ƒëi·ªÉm, so `pass_score`, qu·∫£n l√Ω `attempt_no` vs `max_attempts`. |\\n| `CertificateService` | Khi ƒë·∫°t: sinh `certificate_code` (unique), render PDF (dompdf), l∆∞u `pdf_path`. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 4. Data model (MySQL)\\n\\n14 b·∫£ng nghi·ªáp v·ª•. Ngo√Ýi ra Laravel/Sanctum t·ª± t·∫°o: `personal_access_tokens` (Sanctum), `password_reset_tokens`, `sessions`, `cache`, `jobs`, `failed_jobs`.\\n\\nK√Ω hi·ªáu: **PK** = kh√≥a ch√≠nh (id, bigint auto-increment), **FK** = kh√≥a ngo·∫°i, *ts* = `created_at`/`updated_at`.\\n\\n### 4.1. `users`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| name | varchar | not null |\\n| email | varchar | **unique**, not null |\\n| email_verified_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| password | varchar | not null (hashed) |\\n| role | enum('student','admin') | default 'student' |\\n| phone | varchar | nullable |\\n| avatar | varchar | nullable (URL) |\\n| status | enum('active','locked') | default 'active' |\\n| remember_token | varchar | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.2. `categories`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| name | varchar | not null |\\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\\n| description | text | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.3. `courses`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| category_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí categories, index |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\\n| description | longtext | nullable |\\n| thumbnail | varchar | nullable |\\n| price | decimal(10,2) | default 0 |\\n| instructor_name | varchar | nullable |\\n| instructor_bio | text | nullable |\\n| level | enum('beginner','intermediate','advanced') | nullable |\\n| status | enum('draft','published') | default 'draft', index |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.4. `lessons`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| video_url | varchar | not null (embed YouTube/Vimeo) |\\n| description | text | nullable |\\n| duration | int | nullable (gi√¢y) |\\n| position | int | not null (th·ª© t·ª± trong kh√≥a) |\\n| *ts* | | index `(course_id, position)` |\\n\\n### 4.5. `orders`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| amount | decimal(10,2) | not null (snapshot gi√° l√∫c mua) |\\n| status | enum('pending','paid','failed') | default 'pending', index |\\n| payment_method | enum('card','qr') | nullable |\\n| transaction_ref | varchar | nullable |\\n| paid_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | index `(user_id, status)` |\\n\\n### 4.6. `enrollments`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| order_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí orders, nullable |\\n| enrolled_at | timestamp | not null |\\n| expires_at | timestamp | not null (= enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm) |\\n| status | enum('active','expired') | default 'active' |\\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`**, index `expires_at` |\\n\\n### 4.7. `lesson_progress`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\\n| lesson_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí lessons |\\n| is_completed | boolean | default false |\\n| completed_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | **unique `(enrollment_id, lesson_id)`** |\\n\\n### 4.8. `quizzes`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, **unique** (1 b√Ýi thi cu·ªëi/kh√≥a) |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| pass_score | int | default 75 (%) |\\n| max_attempts | int | default 3 |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.9. `questions`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes, index |\\n| content | text | not null |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.10. `question_options`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bi...[truncated]"},"sessionId":"f6391857-cae2-462f-9b72-4aef8b29d817","timestamp":"2026-07-10T16:12:19.817Z","toolInput":{"content":"# SEONGON LMS ‚Äî Backend / System Design Spec\n\n- **Ng√Ýy:** 2026-07-10\n- **Tr·∫°ng th√°i:** Draft (ch·ªù review)\n- **Ph·∫°m vi t√Ýi li·ªáu:** Ki·∫øn tr√∫c h·ªá th·ªëng, data model, **API contract (ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω)**, business rules, payment seam, auth, certificate, v√Ý **to√Ýn b·ªô Docker/Infra**.\n- **Kh√¥ng thu·ªôc t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy:** Chi ti·∫øt frontend React (n·∫±m ·ªü `2026-07-10-seongon-lms-frontend-design.md`). ·ªû ƒë√¢y frontend ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi chung l√Ý \"SPA client\".\n- **ƒê·∫∑c t·∫£ g·ªëc:** [`SPEC/Draft.md`](../../../SPEC/Draft.md) (User Story, actors, s∆° ƒë·ªì Use Case H√¨nh 3.4, Activity H√¨nh 3.1 & 3.2).\n\n---\n\n## 1. T·ªïng quan & m·ª•c ti√™u\n\nSEONGON LMS l√Ý n·ªÅn t·∫£ng **b√°n v√Ý h·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc tr·ª±c tuy·∫øn** cho c√¥ng ty SEONGON. Backend l√Ý m·ªôt **REST API** (Laravel 12) ph·ª•c v·ª• m·ªôt SPA client t√°ch r·ªùi, d·ªØ li·ªáu l∆∞u trong **MySQL 8**.\n\n**3 t√°c nh√¢n (actors):**\n\n| Actor | M√¥ t·∫£ | Tr·∫°ng th√°i auth |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Guest (Kh√°ch)** | Xem/t√¨m kh√≥a h·ªçc, xem chi ti·∫øt, ƒëƒÉng k√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | Ch∆∞a ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p (kh√¥ng token) |\n| **Student (H·ªçc vi√™n)** | Mua kh√≥a (thanh to√°n mock), h·ªçc video, theo d√µi ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (ƒë·∫°t ‚â• 75%), nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ, ƒë√°nh gi√° | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=student` |\n| **Admin (Qu·∫£n tr·ªã vi√™n)** | Qu·∫£n l√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, danh m·ª•c, kh√≥a h·ªçc, b√Ýi h·ªçc, b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra/ng√¢n h√Ýng c√¢u h·ªèi, ƒë√°nh gi√°, dashboard th·ªëng k√™ | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=admin` |\n\n**M·ª•c ti√™u backend:** cung c·∫•p API ƒë·∫ßy ƒë·ªß cho to√Ýn b·ªô User Story trong SPEC, th·ª±c thi ƒë√∫ng c√°c business rule (enrollment 1 nƒÉm, ch·∫∑n thi khi ch∆∞a 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, ng∆∞·ª°ng ƒë·∫°t 75%, c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ), v√Ý c√≥ th·ªÉ test t·ª± ƒë·ªông ƒë∆∞·ª£c.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Tech stack (Backend)\n\n| Th√Ýnh ph·∫ßn | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\n|---|---|\n| Ng√¥n ng·ªØ / Framework | PHP 8.3 ¬∑ **Laravel 12** |\n| Auth | **Laravel Sanctum** (Bearer token cho SPA t√°ch origin) |\n| Database | **MySQL 8** |\n| PDF ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` |\n| Test | **Pest** (tr√™n PHPUnit) + factories + seeders |\n| Ch·∫°y local | Docker Compose (mysql) + `php artisan serve`, ho·∫∑c full-docker |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Ki·∫øn tr√∫c & t·ªï ch·ª©c code\n\n**Ki·ªÉu ki·∫øn tr√∫c: layered chu·∫©n Laravel.** Lu·ªìng m·ªôt request:\n\n```\nRoute (/api/v1/...) ‚Üí Controller (m·ªèng) ‚Üí FormRequest (validate)\n      ‚Üí Service (business logic) ‚Üí Eloquent Model ‚Üí DB\n      ‚Üí API Resource (ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng JSON response)\nAuthorization: middleware (auth:sanctum, role:admin) + Policy\n```\n\nController ch·ªâ ƒëi·ªÅu ph·ªëi; **to√Ýn b·ªô nghi·ªáp v·ª• n·∫±m trong Service** ƒë·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng v√Ý test ƒë·ªôc l·∫≠p.\n\n**B·ªë c·ª•c th∆∞ m·ª•c `BE/app/`:**\n\n```\napp/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Http/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Controllers/Api/\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Public/      # Auth (register/login), Course, Category c√¥ng khai\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Student/     # Order, Enrollment, Lesson, Quiz, Review, Certificate\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Admin/       # User, Category, Course, Lesson, Quiz, Question, Review, Dashboard\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Requests/        # FormRequest cho t·ª´ng action (validate)\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Resources/       # API Resource (CourseResource, LessonResource, ...)\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Middleware/       # EnsureRole (role:admin)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Models/              # Eloquent models + quan h·ªá\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Services/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ EnrollmentService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ProgressService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ QuizGradingService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CertificateService.php\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Payment/\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentGateway.php      # interface\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ MockGateway.php         # implementation hi·ªán t·∫°i\n‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentResult.php       # DTO k·∫øt qu·∫£\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Policies/            # EnrollmentPolicy, ReviewPolicy, ...\n```\n\n**C√°c Service v√Ý tr√°ch nhi·ªám:**\n\n| Service | Tr√°ch nhi·ªám |\n|---|---|\n| `EnrollmentService` | Sau khi order `paid`: t·∫°o `enrollment` v·ªõi `enrolled_at = now`, `expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `status = active`. Ki·ªÉm tra h·∫øt h·∫°n. |\n| `Payment\\PaymentGateway` (interface) + `MockGateway` | X·ª≠ l√Ω thanh to√°n gi·∫£ l·∫≠p, tr·∫£ `PaymentResult` (success/failure). Seam ƒë·ªÉ thay driver th·∫≠t sau. |\n| `ProgressService` | Ghi nh·∫≠n ho√Ýn th√Ýnh lesson, t√≠nh `progress% = completed / total`, ki·ªÉm tra ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán ƒë·ªß 100% ƒë·ªÉ m·ªü b√Ýi thi. |\n| `QuizGradingService` | Ch·∫•m b√Ýi, t√≠nh ƒëi·ªÉm, so `pass_score`, qu·∫£n l√Ω `attempt_no` vs `max_attempts`. |\n| `CertificateService` | Khi ƒë·∫°t: sinh `certificate_code` (unique), render PDF (dompdf), l∆∞u `pdf_path`. |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Data model (MySQL)\n\n14 b·∫£ng nghi·ªáp v·ª•. Ngo√Ýi ra Laravel/Sanctum t·ª± t·∫°o: `personal_access_tokens` (Sanctum), `password_reset_tokens`, `sessions`, `cache`, `jobs`, `failed_jobs`.\n\nK√Ω hi·ªáu: **PK** = kh√≥a ch√≠nh (id, bigint auto-increment), **FK** = kh√≥a ngo·∫°i, *ts* = `created_at`/`updated_at`.\n\n### 4.1. `users`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| name | varchar | not null |\n| email | varchar | **unique**, not null |\n| email_verified_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| password | varchar | not null (hashed) |\n| role | enum('student','admin') | default 'student' |\n| phone | varchar | nullable |\n| avatar | varchar | nullable (URL) |\n| status | enum('active','locked') | default 'active' |\n| remember_token | varchar | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.2. `categories`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| name | varchar | not null |\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\n| description | text | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.3. `courses`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| category_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí categories, index |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\n| description | longtext | nullable |\n| thumbnail | varchar | nullable |\n| price | decimal(10,2) | default 0 |\n| instructor_name | varchar | nullable |\n| instructor_bio | text | nullable |\n| level | enum('beginner','intermediate','advanced') | nullable |\n| status | enum('draft','published') | default 'draft', index |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.4. `lessons`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| video_url | varchar | not null (embed YouTube/Vimeo) |\n| description | text | nullable |\n| duration | int | nullable (gi√¢y) |\n| position | int | not null (th·ª© t·ª± trong kh√≥a) |\n| *ts* | | index `(course_id, position)` |\n\n### 4.5. `orders`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| amount | decimal(10,2) | not null (snapshot gi√° l√∫c mua) |\n| status | enum('pending','paid','failed') | default 'pending', index |\n| payment_method | enum('card','qr') | nullable |\n| transaction_ref | varchar | nullable |\n| paid_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| *ts* | | index `(user_id, status)` |\n\n### 4.6. `enrollments`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\n| order_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí orders, nullable |\n| enrolled_at | timestamp | not null |\n| expires_at | timestamp | not null (= enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm) |\n| status | enum('active','expired') | default 'active' |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`**, index `expires_at` |\n\n### 4.7. `lesson_progress`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\n| lesson_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí lessons |\n| is_completed | boolean | default false |\n| completed_at | timestamp | nullable |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(enrollment_id, lesson_id)`** |\n\n### 4.8. `quizzes`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, **unique** (1 b√Ýi thi cu·ªëi/kh√≥a) |\n| title | varchar | not null |\n| pass_score | int | default 75 (%) |\n| max_attempts | int | default 3 |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.9. `questions`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes, index |\n| content | text | not null |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.10. `question_options`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| question_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí questions, index |\n| content | varchar | not null |\n| is_correct | boolean | default false |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.11. `quiz_attempts`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes |\n| score | int | not null (0‚Äì100) |\n| passed | boolean | not null |\n| attempt_no | int | not null (l·∫ßn thi th·ª© m·∫•y) |\n| submitted_at | timestamp | not null |\n| *ts* | | index `(enrollment_id, quiz_id)` |\n\n### 4.12. `quiz_attempt_answers`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| quiz_attempt_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quiz_attempts |\n| question_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí questions |\n| selected_option_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí question_options, nullable |\n| is_correct | boolean | not null |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.13. `reviews`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, index |\n| rating | tinyint | 1‚Äì5, not null |\n| comment | text | nullable |\n| status | enum('visible','hidden') | default 'visible' |\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`** |\n\n### 4.14. `certificates`\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\n|---|---|---|\n| id | bigint | PK |\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments, **unique** |\n| certificate_code | varchar | **unique** (vd `SEONGON-2026-000123`) |\n| issued_at | timestamp | not null |\n| pdf_path | varchar | nullable |\n| *ts* | | |\n\n### 4.15. Quan h·ªá (relationships)\n\n- **User** hasMany `orders`, `enrollments`, `reviews`.\n- **Category** hasMany `courses`.\n- **Course** belongsTo `category`; hasMany `lessons`, `orders`, `enrollments`, `reviews`; hasOne `quiz`.\n- **Lesson** belongsTo `course`; hasMany `lesson_progress`.\n- **Order** belongsTo `user`, `course`; hasOne `enrollment`.\n- **Enrollment** belongsTo `user`, `course`, `order`; hasMany `lesson_progress`, `quiz_attempts`; hasOne `certificate`.\n- **Quiz** belongsTo `course`; hasMany `questions`, `quiz_attempts`.\n- **Question** belongsTo `quiz`; hasMany `question_options`.\n- **QuizAttempt** belongsTo `enrollment`, `quiz`; hasMany `quiz_attempt_answers`.\n- **Review** belongsTo `user`, `course`.\n- **Certificate** belongsTo `enrollment`.\n\n---\n\n## 5. API contract (`/api/v1`) ‚Äî AUTHORITATIVE\n\nƒê√¢y l√Ý ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω cho to√Ýn b·ªô endpoint. Frontend spec ch·ªâ tham chi·∫øu, kh√¥ng ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l·∫°i.\n\n**Quy ∆∞·ªõc chung:**\n- Base URL: `/api/v1`. Response JSON.\n- Auth: header `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.\n- Danh s√°ch c√≥ ph√¢n trang: `{ data: [...], meta: { current_page, last_page, per_page, total } }`.\n- L·ªói: `422` (validation, k√®m `errors`), `401` (ch∆∞a auth), `403` (kh√¥ng ƒë·ªß quy·ªÅn / kh√≥a h·∫øt h·∫°n), `404` (kh√¥ng t·ªìn t·∫°i). Envelope l·ªói: `{ message, errors? }`.\n\n### 5.1. Public (kh√¥ng c·∫ßn auth)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/auth/register` | ƒêƒÉng k√Ω h·ªçc vi√™n | `{name,email,password,password_confirmation}` | `{user, token}` |\n| POST | `/auth/login` | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p | `{email,password}` | `{user, token}` |\n| GET | `/categories` | Danh s√°ch danh m·ª•c | ‚Äî | `[category]` |\n| GET | `/courses` | Danh s√°ch + t√¨m ki·∫øm/l·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc `published` | query: `q, category, min_price, max_price, sort, page` | paginated `[course]` |\n| GET | `/courses/{slug}` | Chi ti·∫øt kh√≥a (k√®m lessons preview, quiz info, rating t·ªïng) | ‚Äî | `course` |\n| GET | `/courses/{slug}/reviews` | ƒê√°nh gi√° c·ªßa kh√≥a (ch·ªâ `visible`) | query: `page` | paginated `[review]` |\n\n### 5.2. Authenticated (student | admin)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/auth/logout` | Thu h·ªìi token hi·ªán t·∫°i | ‚Äî | `204` |\n| GET | `/auth/me` | Th√¥ng tin user ƒëang ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | ‚Äî | `user` |\n| PUT | `/auth/profile` | C·∫≠p nh·∫≠t h·ªì s∆° | `{name,phone,avatar?}` | `user` |\n| PUT | `/auth/password` | ƒê·ªïi m·∫≠t kh·∫©u | `{current_password,password,password_confirmation}` | `204` |\n\n### 5.3. Student\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ | Req | Resp |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/orders` | T·∫°o ƒë∆°n mua kh√≥a (status `pending`) | `{course_id}` | `order` |\n| POST | `/orders/{id}/pay` | Thanh to√°n (mock) | `{payment_method:'card'|'qr', outcome?:'success'|'failure'}` | `{order, enrollment?}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses` | Kh√≥a ƒë√£ ƒëƒÉng k√Ω (k√®m progress, tr·∫°ng th√°i h·∫øt h·∫°n) | query: `page` | paginated `[enrollment+course]` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/lessons` | B√Ýi h·ªçc c·ªßa kh√≥a + tr·∫°ng th√°i ho√Ýn th√Ýnh | ‚Äî | `[lesson+is_completed]` |\n| POST | `/my/lessons/{lesson}/complete` | ƒê√°nh d·∫•u ho√Ýn th√Ýnh 1 lesson | ‚Äî | `{progress}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/progress` | Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô (%), ƒë·ªß ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán thi ch∆∞a | ‚Äî | `{completed,total,percent,can_take_exam}` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/quiz` | ƒê·ªÅ thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (c√¢u h·ªèi + options, **·∫©n** `is_correct`) | ‚Äî | `quiz+questions` |\n| POST | `/my/courses/{course}/quiz/attempts` | N·ªôp b√Ýi thi, ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm | `{answers:[{question_id,option_id}]}` | `{attempt, passed, score, certificate?}` |\n| GET | `/my/quiz-attempts/{attempt}` | Xem k·∫øt qu·∫£ chi ti·∫øt (ƒë√∫ng/sai t·ª´ng c√¢u) | ‚Äî | `attempt+answers` |\n| POST | `/my/courses/{course}/reviews` | ƒê√°nh gi√° kh√≥a (sau khi c√≥ enrollment) | `{rating,comment?}` | `review` |\n| GET | `/my/courses/{course}/certificate` | T·∫£i ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ PDF | ‚Äî | `application/pdf` |\n\n### 5.4. Admin (`/admin`, middleware `role:admin`)\n| Method | Path | M√¥ t·∫£ |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/admin/users` | Danh s√°ch h·ªçc vi√™n (filter/search) |\n| PATCH | `/admin/users/{id}/status` | K√≠ch ho·∫°t / kh√≥a t√Ýi kho·∫£n (`{status}`) |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/categories` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/categories/{id}` | CRUD danh m·ª•c |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/courses` ¬∑ GET/PUT/DELETE `/admin/courses/{id}` | CRUD kh√≥a h·ªçc |\n| PATCH | `/admin/courses/{id}/publish` | Xu·∫•t b·∫£n / ·∫©n kh√≥a (`{status}`) |\n| GET/POST | `/admin/courses/{course}/lessons` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/lessons/{id}` | CRUD b√Ýi h·ªçc |\n| PATCH | `/admin/courses/{course}/lessons/reorder` | S·∫Øp x·∫øp l·∫°i th·ª© t·ª± (`{order:[lesson_id...]}`) |\n| POST/PUT | `/admin/courses/{course}/quiz` | T·∫°o/s·ª≠a b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra (title, pass_score, max_attempts) |\n| POST | `/admin/quizzes/{quiz}/questions` ¬∑ PUT/DELETE `/admin/questions/{id}` | CRUD c√¢u h·ªèi + ƒë√°p √°n (options l·ªìng trong payload) |\n| GET | `/admin/reviews` ¬∑ PATCH `/admin/reviews/{id}/status` ¬∑ DELETE `/admin/reviews/{id}` | Duy·ªát/·∫©n/x√≥a ƒë√°nh gi√° |\n| GET | `/admin/dashboard/stats` | Th·ªëng k√™: s·ªë h·ªçc vi√™n, s·ªë kh√≥a, t·ª∑ l·ªá ho√Ýn th√Ýnh, doanh thu (t·ªïng `orders.amount` v·ªõi `status=paid`) |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Business rules\n\n√Ånh x·∫° tr·ª±c ti·∫øp c√°c s∆° ƒë·ªì Activity trong SPEC (H√¨nh 3.1 ‚Äì thanh to√°n, H√¨nh 3.2 ‚Äì h·ªçc).\n\n**BR-1 ‚Äî Mua kh√≥a & thanh to√°n (H√¨nh 3.1):**\n1. `POST /orders` t·∫°o order `pending` (amount = gi√° kh√≥a hi·ªán t·∫°i).\n2. `POST /orders/{id}/pay` g·ªçi `MockGateway`.\n   - **Success:** order ‚Üí `paid` + `paid_at`; `EnrollmentService` t·∫°o `enrollment` (`expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `active`); (song song, theo s∆° ƒë·ªì fork/join) ghi nh·∫≠n v√Ý g·ª≠i th√¥ng b√°o + h√≥a ƒë∆°n (mock/log/notification). Tr·∫£ v·ªÅ `{order, enrollment}`.\n   - **Failure:** order ‚Üí `failed`; h·ªçc vi√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ **th·ª≠ l·∫°i** (`pay` l·∫ßn n·ªØa) ho·∫∑c **h·ªßy** (d·ª´ng lu·ªìng). Tr·∫£ `422/200` k√®m th√¥ng b√°o l·ªói.\n3. Kh√¥ng cho mua n·∫øu ƒë√£ c√≥ enrollment `active` cho kh√≥a ƒë√≥ (unique `(user_id,course_id)`).\n\n**BR-2 ‚Äî Gating truy c·∫≠p h·ªçc:** m·ªçi endpoint `/my/courses/{course}/*` y√™u c·∫ßu enrollment `active` **v√Ý** `expires_at >= now`. N·∫øu `expires_at < now` ‚Üí ƒë√°nh d·∫•u `expired` ‚Üí tr·∫£ `403` (\"kh√≥a ƒë√£ h·∫øt h·∫°n\"). (H√¨nh 3.2, nh√°nh \"Kh√≥a h·ªçc c√≤n h·∫°n?\").\n\n**BR-3 ‚Äî Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô:** `POST /my/lessons/{lesson}/complete` upsert `lesson_progress.is_completed = true`. `progress% = s·ªë lesson completed / t·ªïng lesson c·ªßa kh√≥a`.\n\n**BR-4 ‚Äî Gating thi:** ch·ªâ cho ph√©p `POST .../quiz/attempts` khi `progress = 100%` (`can_take_exam = true`). Ch∆∞a ƒë·ªß ‚Üí `403`. (H√¨nh 3.2, nh√°nh \"ƒê·∫°t 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô?\").\n\n**BR-5 ‚Äî Ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm:** `score = (s·ªë c√¢u ƒë√∫ng / t·ªïng c√¢u) * 100`. `passed = score >= quiz.pass_score` (m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh **75**). `attempt_no` tƒÉng d·∫ßn; n·∫øu `attempt_no > max_attempts` ‚Üí ch·∫∑n n·ªôp th√™m (`422`). Ch∆∞a ƒë·∫°t ‚Üí th√¥ng b√°o cho thi l·∫°i (trong gi·ªõi h·∫°n `max_attempts`). (H√¨nh 3.2, \"ƒêi·ªÉm thi ‚â• 75%?\").\n\n**BR-6 ‚Äî C·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ:** l·∫ßn **ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n** `passed = true`, `CertificateService` t·∫°o `certificate` (`certificate_code` unique) + render PDF. Idempotent: ƒë√£ c√≥ ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ th√¨ kh√¥ng t·∫°o l·∫°i.\n\n**BR-7 ‚Äî ƒê√°nh gi√°:** `POST .../reviews` l√Ý **t√πy ch·ªçn**, cho h·ªçc vi√™n ƒë√£ c√≥ enrollment; unique `(user_id, course_id)` (m·ªói kh√≥a ƒë√°nh gi√° 1 l·∫ßn, c√≥ th·ªÉ c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t).\n\n> **‚öÝÔ∏è M√¢u thu·∫´n trong SPEC (gi·ªØ l·∫°i ƒë·ªÉ ƒë·ªëi chi·∫øu):** ph·∫ßn vƒÉn b·∫£n ¬ß3.2.2.2 n√≥i h·ªçc vi√™n \"*ph·∫£i ƒë√°nh gi√° kh√≥a h·ªçc ƒë·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ*\", nh∆∞ng **s∆° ƒë·ªì H√¨nh 3.2 v·∫Ω ng∆∞·ª£c l·∫°i**: c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ **tr∆∞·ªõc**, r·ªìi ƒë√°nh gi√° l√Ý b∆∞·ªõc **t√πy ch·ªçn cu·ªëi**. ‚Üí Tri·ªÉn khai **theo s∆° ƒë·ªì** (cert tr∆∞·ªõc, rating optional). N·∫øu c√¥ng ty mu·ªën theo vƒÉn b·∫£n, ch·ªâ c·∫ßn ƒë·∫£o th·ª© t·ª± ·ªü BR-6/BR-7 ‚Äî ghi nh·∫≠n l√Ý ƒëi·ªÉm c·∫ßn ch·ªët v·ªõi PM.\n\n---\n\n## 7. Payment seam (mock, c√≥ th·ªÉ thay)\n\nThanh to√°n ƒë∆∞·ª£c tr·ª´u t∆∞·ª£ng h√≥a ƒë·ªÉ **kh√¥ng kh√≥a c·ª©ng** v√Ýo m·ªôt c·ªïng c·ª• th·ªÉ:\n\n```php\ninterface PaymentGateway {\n    public function charge(Order $order, array $data): PaymentResult;\n}\n\nfinal class PaymentResult {\n    public bool $success;\n    public ?string $transactionRef;\n    public ?string $message;\n}\n```\n\n- **`MockGateway`** (driver hi·ªán t·∫°i): quy·∫øt ƒë·ªãnh success/failure theo input `outcome` (m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng dev/demo); sinh `transaction_ref` gi·∫£. Kh√¥ng g·ªçi m·∫°ng.\n- ƒêƒÉng k√Ω qua container: `PaymentGateway::class ‚Üí MockGateway::class` trong `AppServiceProvider`.\n- **VNPay l√Ý driver t∆∞∆°ng lai** (`VnpayGateway implements PaymentGateway`): ch·ªâ c·∫ßn th√™m class + ƒë·ªïi binding, **kh√¥ng s·ª≠a** `EnrollmentService`/controller. **Kh√¥ng thi·∫øt k·∫ø chi ti·∫øt VNPay ·ªü giai ƒëo·∫°n n√Ýy (YAGNI).**\n\n---\n\n## 8. Auth & ph√¢n quy·ªÅn\n\n- **Sanctum token:** `register`/`login` tr·∫£ `{user, token}` (`personal_access_tokens`). Client g·ª≠i `Authorization: Bearer <token>`. `logout` thu h·ªìi token hi·ªán t·∫°i.\n- **Roles:** `student` (m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh khi ƒëƒÉng k√Ω) v√Ý `admin` (t·∫°o qua seeder, kh√¥ng ƒëƒÉng k√Ω c√¥ng khai). Guest = request kh√¥ng c√≥ token.\n- **Middleware `role:admin`** (`EnsureRole`) b·∫£o v·ªá nh√≥m `/admin/*`.\n- **Policies:** `EnrollmentPolicy` (h·ªçc vi√™n ch·ªâ truy c·∫≠p enrollment/kh√≥a c·ªßa ch√≠nh m√¨nh), `ReviewPolicy`. Ki·ªÉm tra tr·∫°ng th√°i t√Ýi kho·∫£n: `status=locked` ‚Üí ch·∫∑n ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p/t·ª´ ch·ªëi request (`403`).\n\n---\n\n## 9. Certificate (ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ)\n\n- K√≠ch ho·∫°t t·∫°i BR-6. `certificate_code` ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng `SEONGON-{year}-{seq}` (unique).\n- Render PDF b·∫±ng `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` t·ª´ Blade template (t√™n h·ªçc vi√™n, t√™n kh√≥a, ng√Ýy c·∫•p, m√£ ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ). L∆∞u `pdf_path` (storage) ho·∫∑c render on-the-fly.\n- `GET /my/courses/{course}/certificate` tr·∫£ file PDF (ch·ªâ ch·ªß s·ªü h·ªØu enrollment).\n\n---\n\n## 10. Infra / Docker\n\n`Infra/docker-compose.yml` (t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy s·ªü h·ªØu to√Ýn b·ªô ph·∫ßn Docker):\n\n| Service | Image / Build | Vai tr√≤ | Port |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `mysql` | `mysql:8.0` | Database. Env: `MYSQL_DATABASE=seongon_lms`, `MYSQL_USER`, `MYSQL_PASSWORD`, `MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD`. Volume `mysql_data`. | 3306 |\n| `backend` | build `Infra/backend.Dockerfile` (PHP 8.3-fpm + composer, nginx) ‚Äî ho·∫∑c dev: `php artisan serve`. Mount `../BE`. | Laravel API | 8000 |\n| `frontend` | `node:22` (Vite dev) ho·∫∑c build ‚Üí nginx serve. Mount `../FE`. | SPA client | 5173 (dev) / 80 (prod) |\n| `phpmyadmin` *(t√πy ch·ªçn)* | `phpmyadmin` | Qu·∫£n tr·ªã DB qua web | 8080 |\n\n**Bi·∫øn m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng ch√≠nh (`BE/.env`):** `APP_URL=http://localhost:8000`, `DB_CONNECTION=mysql`, `DB_HOST=mysql` (trong docker) / `127.0.0.1` (local), `DB_DATABASE=seongon_lms`, `DB_USERNAME`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `SANCTUM_STATEFUL_DOMAINS`, `FRONTEND_URL`.\n\n**Hai c√°ch ch·∫°y dev:**\n1. **Full-docker:** `docker compose up` ‚Äî c·∫£ mysql + backend + frontend.\n2. **Nh·∫π:** ch·ªâ ch·∫°y `mysql` b·∫±ng Docker, c√≤n `php artisan serve` (BE) v√Ý `npm run dev` (FE) ch·∫°y tr·ª±c ti·∫øp tr√™n m√°y.\n\nCORS c·∫•u h√¨nh cho ph√©p origin c·ªßa FE (`http://localhost:5173`).\n\n---\n\n## 11. Testing (Backend)\n\n**Pest feature tests** (ch·∫°y tr√™n DB test, m·ªói test refresh). Danh s√°ch t·ªëi thi·ªÉu:\n\n| Nh√≥m | Test |\n|---|---|\n| Auth | register t·∫°o user+token; login ƒë√∫ng/sai; login khi `locked` b·ªã ch·∫∑n; ƒë·ªïi m·∫≠t kh·∫©u; logout thu h·ªìi token |\n| Catalog | list courses ch·ªâ `published`; filter theo `q`/`category`/kho·∫£ng gi√°; chi ti·∫øt theo slug |\n| Mua kh√≥a | t·∫°o order pending; pay **success** ‚Üí order paid + t·∫°o enrollment 1 nƒÉm; pay **failure** ‚Üí order failed, cho retry; kh√¥ng cho mua tr√πng khi ƒë√£ enroll |\n| Enrollment | `expires_at = enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm`; d√πng `travel()` gi·∫£ l·∫≠p qu√° 1 nƒÉm ‚Üí truy c·∫≠p h·ªçc tr·∫£ `403` |\n| Ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô | complete lesson c·∫≠p nh·∫≠t progress%; unique kh√¥ng nh√¢n ƒë√¥i |\n| Thi | ch·∫∑n thi khi progress < 100%; ch·∫•m ƒëi·ªÉm ƒë√∫ng; `passed` khi ‚â•75%; `attempt_no` tƒÉng; ch·∫∑n khi v∆∞·ª£t `max_attempts` |\n| Ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | ƒë·∫°t l·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ‚Üí t·∫°o certificate + code unique; ƒë√£ c√≥ th√¨ kh√¥ng t·∫°o l·∫°i; ch·ªâ ch·ªß s·ªü h·ªØu t·∫£i ƒë∆∞·ª£c |\n| Review | t·∫°o review unique theo (user,course) |\n| Admin & ph√¢n quy·ªÅn | CRUD category/course/lesson/quiz/question; `role:admin` ch·∫∑n student; dashboard stats tr·∫£ ƒë√∫ng s·ªë li·ªáu |\n\n**Fixtures:** Factories cho m·ªçi model; **Seeder** t·∫°o s·∫µn 1 admin, v√Ýi category, v√Ýi course + lessons + 1 quiz + questions/options ƒë·ªÉ dev/demo.\n\n---\n\n## 12. Non-goals / h∆∞·ªõng m·ªü r·ªông\n\n- T√≠ch h·ª£p c·ªïng thanh to√°n th·∫≠t (VNPay/MoMo) ‚Äî ch·ªâ ch·ª´a seam.\n- Upload/stream video (S3/MinIO) ‚Äî hi·ªán d√πng embed URL.\n- ƒêa ng√¥n ng·ªØ (i18n), th√¥ng b√°o real-time, email th·∫≠t (hi·ªán log/notification mock).\n- H·ªçc vi√™n nhi·ªÅu vai tr√≤ / ph√¢n quy·ªÅn chi ti·∫øt (RBAC n√¢ng cao) ‚Äî hi·ªán 2 role ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n.\n\n---\n\n## Ph·ª• l·ª•c ‚Äî quy·∫øt ƒë·ªãnh ƒë√£ ch·ªët\n\n| H·∫°ng m·ª•c | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\n|---|---|\n| Backend | Laravel 12, PHP 8.3, Sanctum token |\n| Database | MySQL 8 |\n| Payment | Mock (seam `PaymentGateway`, VNPay ƒë·ªÉ sau) |\n| Video | Embed URL (YouTube/Vimeo) |\n| Ki·∫øn tr√∫c code | Layered: Controller ‚Üí FormRequest ‚Üí Service ‚Üí Model ‚Üí Resource |\n| Frontend | (t√Ýi li·ªáu ri√™ng) React 19 + Vite + TS + Tailwind |\n","file_path":"D:\\CODE\\seongon-lms\\docs\\superpowers\\specs\\2026-07-10-seongon-lms-backend-design.md"},"toolName":"Write","toolOutput":"{\"type\":\"create\",\"filePath\":\"D:/CODE/seongon-lms/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-10-seongon-lms-backend-design.md\",\"content\":\"# SEONGON LMS ‚Äî Backend / System Design Spec\\n\\n- **Ng√Ýy:** 2026-07-10\\n- **Tr·∫°ng th√°i:** Draft (ch·ªù review)\\n- **Ph·∫°m vi t√Ýi li·ªáu:** Ki·∫øn tr√∫c h·ªá th·ªëng, data model, **API contract (ngu·ªìn ch√¢n l√Ω)**, business rules, payment seam, auth, certificate, v√Ý **to√Ýn b·ªô Docker/Infra**.\\n- **Kh√¥ng thu·ªôc t√Ýi li·ªáu n√Ýy:** Chi ti·∫øt frontend React (n·∫±m ·ªü `2026-07-10-seongon-lms-frontend-design.md`). ·ªû ƒë√¢y frontend ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi chung l√Ý \\\"SPA client\\\".\\n- **ƒê·∫∑c t·∫£ g·ªëc:** [`SPEC/Draft.md`](../../../SPEC/Draft.md) (User Story, actors, s∆° ƒë·ªì Use Case H√¨nh 3.4, Activity H√¨nh 3.1 & 3.2).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. T·ªïng quan & m·ª•c ti√™u\\n\\nSEONGON LMS l√Ý n·ªÅn t·∫£ng **b√°n v√Ý h·ªçc kh√≥a h·ªçc tr·ª±c tuy·∫øn** cho c√¥ng ty SEONGON. Backend l√Ý m·ªôt **REST API** (Laravel 12) ph·ª•c v·ª• m·ªôt SPA client t√°ch r·ªùi, d·ªØ li·ªáu l∆∞u trong **MySQL 8**.\\n\\n**3 t√°c nh√¢n (actors):**\\n\\n| Actor | M√¥ t·∫£ | Tr·∫°ng th√°i auth |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| **Guest (Kh√°ch)** | Xem/t√¨m kh√≥a h·ªçc, xem chi ti·∫øt, ƒëƒÉng k√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p | Ch∆∞a ƒëƒÉng nh·∫≠p (kh√¥ng token) |\\n| **Student (H·ªçc vi√™n)** | Mua kh√≥a (thanh to√°n mock), h·ªçc video, theo d√µi ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, thi cu·ªëi kh√≥a (ƒë·∫°t ‚â• 75%), nh·∫≠n ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ, ƒë√°nh gi√° | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=student` |\\n| **Admin (Qu·∫£n tr·ªã vi√™n)** | Qu·∫£n l√Ω t√Ýi kho·∫£n, danh m·ª•c, kh√≥a h·ªçc, b√Ýi h·ªçc, b√Ýi ki·ªÉm tra/ng√¢n h√Ýng c√¢u h·ªèi, ƒë√°nh gi√°, dashboard th·ªëng k√™ | ƒêƒÉng nh·∫≠p, `role=admin` |\\n\\n**M·ª•c ti√™u backend:** cung c·∫•p API ƒë·∫ßy ƒë·ªß cho to√Ýn b·ªô User Story trong SPEC, th·ª±c thi ƒë√∫ng c√°c business rule (enrollment 1 nƒÉm, ch·∫∑n thi khi ch∆∞a 100% ti·∫øn ƒë·ªô, ng∆∞·ª°ng ƒë·∫°t 75%, c·∫•p ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ), v√Ý c√≥ th·ªÉ test t·ª± ƒë·ªông ƒë∆∞·ª£c.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Tech stack (Backend)\\n\\n| Th√Ýnh ph·∫ßn | L·ª±a ch·ªçn |\\n|---|---|\\n| Ng√¥n ng·ªØ / Framework | PHP 8.3 ¬∑ **Laravel 12** |\\n| Auth | **Laravel Sanctum** (Bearer token cho SPA t√°ch origin) |\\n| Database | **MySQL 8** |\\n| PDF ch·ª©ng ch·ªâ | `barryvdh/laravel-dompdf` |\\n| Test | **Pest** (tr√™n PHPUnit) + factories + seeders |\\n| Ch·∫°y local | Docker Compose (mysql) + `php artisan serve`, ho·∫∑c full-docker |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Ki·∫øn tr√∫c & t·ªï ch·ª©c code\\n\\n**Ki·ªÉu ki·∫øn tr√∫c: layered chu·∫©n Laravel.** Lu·ªìng m·ªôt request:\\n\\n```\\nRoute (/api/v1/...) ‚Üí Controller (m·ªèng) ‚Üí FormRequest (validate)\\n      ‚Üí Service (business logic) ‚Üí Eloquent Model ‚Üí DB\\n      ‚Üí API Resource (ƒë·ªãnh d·∫°ng JSON response)\\nAuthorization: middleware (auth:sanctum, role:admin) + Policy\\n```\\n\\nController ch·ªâ ƒëi·ªÅu ph·ªëi; **to√Ýn b·ªô nghi·ªáp v·ª• n·∫±m trong Service** ƒë·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng v√Ý test ƒë·ªôc l·∫≠p.\\n\\n**B·ªë c·ª•c th∆∞ m·ª•c `BE/app/`:**\\n\\n```\\napp/\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Http/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Controllers/Api/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Public/      # Auth (register/login), Course, Category c√¥ng khai\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Student/     # Order, Enrollment, Lesson, Quiz, Review, Certificate\\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Admin/       # User, Category, Course, Lesson, Quiz, Question, Review, Dashboard\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Requests/        # FormRequest cho t·ª´ng action (validate)\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Resources/       # API Resource (CourseResource, LessonResource, ...)\\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Middleware/       # EnsureRole (role:admin)\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Models/              # Eloquent models + quan h·ªá\\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Services/\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ EnrollmentService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ProgressService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ QuizGradingService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CertificateService.php\\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Payment/\\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentGateway.php      # interface\\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ MockGateway.php         # implementation hi·ªán t·∫°i\\n‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ PaymentResult.php       # DTO k·∫øt qu·∫£\\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Policies/            # EnrollmentPolicy, ReviewPolicy, ...\\n```\\n\\n**C√°c Service v√Ý tr√°ch nhi·ªám:**\\n\\n| Service | Tr√°ch nhi·ªám |\\n|---|---|\\n| `EnrollmentService` | Sau khi order `paid`: t·∫°o `enrollment` v·ªõi `enrolled_at = now`, `expires_at = now + 1 nƒÉm`, `status = active`. Ki·ªÉm tra h·∫øt h·∫°n. |\\n| `Payment\\\\PaymentGateway` (interface) + `MockGateway` | X·ª≠ l√Ω thanh to√°n gi·∫£ l·∫≠p, tr·∫£ `PaymentResult` (success/failure). Seam ƒë·ªÉ thay driver th·∫≠t sau. |\\n| `ProgressService` | Ghi nh·∫≠n ho√Ýn th√Ýnh lesson, t√≠nh `progress% = completed / total`, ki·ªÉm tra ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán ƒë·ªß 100% ƒë·ªÉ m·ªü b√Ýi thi. |\\n| `QuizGradingService` | Ch·∫•m b√Ýi, t√≠nh ƒëi·ªÉm, so `pass_score`, qu·∫£n l√Ω `attempt_no` vs `max_attempts`. |\\n| `CertificateService` | Khi ƒë·∫°t: sinh `certificate_code` (unique), render PDF (dompdf), l∆∞u `pdf_path`. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 4. Data model (MySQL)\\n\\n14 b·∫£ng nghi·ªáp v·ª•. Ngo√Ýi ra Laravel/Sanctum t·ª± t·∫°o: `personal_access_tokens` (Sanctum), `password_reset_tokens`, `sessions`, `cache`, `jobs`, `failed_jobs`.\\n\\nK√Ω hi·ªáu: **PK** = kh√≥a ch√≠nh (id, bigint auto-increment), **FK** = kh√≥a ngo·∫°i, *ts* = `created_at`/`updated_at`.\\n\\n### 4.1. `users`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| name | varchar | not null |\\n| email | varchar | **unique**, not null |\\n| email_verified_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| password | varchar | not null (hashed) |\\n| role | enum('student','admin') | default 'student' |\\n| phone | varchar | nullable |\\n| avatar | varchar | nullable (URL) |\\n| status | enum('active','locked') | default 'active' |\\n| remember_token | varchar | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.2. `categories`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| name | varchar | not null |\\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\\n| description | text | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.3. `courses`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| category_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí categories, index |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| slug | varchar | **unique** |\\n| description | longtext | nullable |\\n| thumbnail | varchar | nullable |\\n| price | decimal(10,2) | default 0 |\\n| instructor_name | varchar | nullable |\\n| instructor_bio | text | nullable |\\n| level | enum('beginner','intermediate','advanced') | nullable |\\n| status | enum('draft','published') | default 'draft', index |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.4. `lessons`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| video_url | varchar | not null (embed YouTube/Vimeo) |\\n| description | text | nullable |\\n| duration | int | nullable (gi√¢y) |\\n| position | int | not null (th·ª© t·ª± trong kh√≥a) |\\n| *ts* | | index `(course_id, position)` |\\n\\n### 4.5. `orders`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| amount | decimal(10,2) | not null (snapshot gi√° l√∫c mua) |\\n| status | enum('pending','paid','failed') | default 'pending', index |\\n| payment_method | enum('card','qr') | nullable |\\n| transaction_ref | varchar | nullable |\\n| paid_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | index `(user_id, status)` |\\n\\n### 4.6. `enrollments`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| user_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí users |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses |\\n| order_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí orders, nullable |\\n| enrolled_at | timestamp | not null |\\n| expires_at | timestamp | not null (= enrolled_at + 1 nƒÉm) |\\n| status | enum('active','expired') | default 'active' |\\n| *ts* | | **unique `(user_id, course_id)`**, index `expires_at` |\\n\\n### 4.7. `lesson_progress`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| enrollment_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí enrollments |\\n| lesson_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí lessons |\\n| is_completed | boolean | default false |\\n| completed_at | timestamp | nullable |\\n| *ts* | | **unique `(enrollment_id, lesson_id)`** |\\n\\n### 4.8. `quizzes`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| course_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí courses, **unique** (1 b√Ýi thi cu·ªëi/kh√≥a) |\\n| title | varchar | not null |\\n| pass_score | int | default 75 (%) |\\n| max_attempts | int | default 3 |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.9. `questions`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bigint | PK |\\n| quiz_id | bigint | **FK** ‚Üí quizzes, index |\\n| content | text | not null |\\n| *ts* | | |\\n\\n### 4.10. `question_options`\\n| C·ªôt | Ki·ªÉu | R√Ýng bu·ªôc |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| id | bi...[truncated]"},"obs_mrf5s64s_428ea7e04168":{"hookType":"post_tool_use","id":"obs_mrf5s64s_428ea7e04168","raw":{"tool_input":{"content":"<?php\n\nuse Illuminate\\Database\\Migrations\\Migration;\nuse Illuminate\\Database\\Schema\\Blueprint;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Schema;\n\nreturn new class extends Migration\n{\n    public function up(): void\n    {\n        Schema::create('reviews', function (Blueprint $table) {\n            $table->id();\n            $table->foreignId('user_id')->constrained()->cascadeOnDelete();\n            $table->foreignId('course_id')->constrained()->cascadeOnDelete();\n            $table->unsignedTinyInteger('rating');\n            $table->text('comment')->nullable();\n            $table->enum('status', ['visible', 'hidden'])->default('visible');\n            $table->timestamps();\n            $table->unique(['user_id', 'course_id']);\n        });\n    }\n\n    public function down(): void\n    {\n        Schema::dropIfExists('reviews');\n    }\n};\n","file_path":"D:\\CODE\\seongon-lms\\BE\\database\\migrations\\2026_07_10_170012_create_reviews_table.php"},"tool_name":"Write","tool_output":{"content":"<?php\n\nuse Illuminate\\Database\\Migrations\\Migration;\nuse Illuminate\\Database\\Schema\\Blueprint;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Fa